text: Varito anu: "Margabhrastatvanlo padi vunnavaniki, ananta karunamayudu, oka samayam varaku vyavadhi nistu untadu. Tudaku varu tamaku vagdanam ceyabadina danini cusinapudu, adi (kathinamaina) siksano kavaccu leda antima ghadiyano kavaccu! Hinasthitilo unna vadevado mariyu balahina vargam (sena) evarido variki teliyagaladu
